peopleAlsoAsk.question: How to clean Giuseppe Armani figurines?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: The standard procedure used by many involves filling a bowl with warm water and a very mild dishwashing liquid. Dip a very soft cloth into the water and gently clean the porcelain figurine until it's free of dirt. Always remember to use a lint free cloth.
